{"tid":724758,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=?? 護老院涉剋扣工資 工友疑接獲恐嚇電話「老闆唔會賠錢，唔好搞咁多事！」","createTime":"2018-07-01T07:34:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-01T07:39:01.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5bdd8b4377b5f7e80725c5e61d3ca34903d3d693","tid":724758,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T07:34:49.000Z","msg":"牛頭角私營安老院「宏光護老有限公司」近日疑剋扣外地勞工工資及假期。協助外勞的社區及院舍照顧員總工會組織幹事曾紀南今日（1日）表示，近日有部份外勞家屬<span style=\"color: violet;\">接獲恐嚇電話，通話中有一位女士說：「老闆唔會賠錢，唔好搞咁多事！」</span>但指出只屬零星事件，目前未有足夠證據印證與宏光護老院有關。<br />\n<br />\n他續稱，由於事件已進入司法程序，料須時3至4個月完成審訊，故現時正與相關外勞商討留港意向或回鄉等候消息，但強調外勞回鄉亦不代表他們放棄投訴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/205526/%E5%AE%8F%E5%85%89%E8%AD%B7%E8%80%81%E9%99%A2%E6%B6%89%E5%89%8B%E6%89%A3%E5%A4%96%E5%8B%9E%E5%B7%A5%E8%B3%87-%E5%80%8B%E5%88%A5%E5%B7%A5%E5%8F%8B%E5%AE%B6%E4%BA%BA%E7%96%91%E6%8E%A5%E7%8D%B2%E6%81%90%E5%9A%87%E9%9B%BB%E8%A9%B1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F205526%2F%25E5%25AE%258F%25E5%2585%2589%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E8%2580%2581%25E9%2599%25A2%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%2589%258B%25E6%2589%25A3%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%258B%259E%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E8%25B3%2587-%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%2588%25A5%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%258F%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%258E%25A5%25E7%258D%25B2%25E6%2581%2590%25E5%259A%2587%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A9%25B1&d=jR4AI4tUEnMBLdsrLzKp4jM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=df3891d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/205526/%E5%AE%8F%E5%85%89%E8%AD%B7%E8%80%81%E9%99%A2%E6%B6%89%E5%89%8B%E6%89%A3%E5%A4%96%E5%8B%9E%E5%B7%A5%E8%B3%87-%E5%80%8B%E5%88%A5%E5%B7%A5%E5%8F%8B%E5%AE%B6%E4%BA%BA%E7%96%91%E6%8E%A5%E7%8D%B2%E6%81%90%E5%9A%87%E9%9B%BB%E8%A9%B1</a>"},{"pid":"cfc7ead1a92faf2ac7a0ef02db717cb74d1eba55","tid":724758,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,